RainbruRPG::Network::tReceivedPacket

RainbruRPG::Network::tReceivedPacket Struct Reference

#include <enetserver.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

A structure defining what is send to the application when a packet is received.

This structure is used in some Qt signals/slots. The peer pointer can be used to send a response to the client.
